howto-interact.name: howto-interact
howto-interact.description:
​
 **How do I start using the bot?**
> 1) You must be discord rank `raider` to talk to Cracked
> 2) You can use ANY channel where you're allowed to write
> 3) Start a command using `/` in the chat field
> 4) Most messages created by the bot can ONLY be seen by you
​
